body:
There's [currently no way](https://discord.com/channels/636084430946959380/742572728787402763/964669144542892032
) to make a SystemVerilog `case` statement `unique` or `priority`.

This would be a useful feature!  This is relevant for generating SystemVerilog using CIRCT for [ROHD](https://github.com/intel/rohd/), and should be applicable to anyone/anything trying to generate these types of `case` statements.
